Variable Name	Isko Value Kaun Deta Hai?	Kab Milti Hai Value?
identityName, plan, flow, source	LCM UI / Requester (Jo access maang raha hai)	Workflow shuru hote hi (At Launch)
approvalSet	"Build Approval Set" Step	Workflow ke chalte waqt beech mein
project	"Compile Project" Step	Workflow ke chalte waqt beech mein
