Approve Step → Manager ke paas request gayi, manager ne "Approve" button dabaya.

action="postApproval" → (Jo aapke code mein abhi hai) → ServiceNow ticket par thappa laga "Approved".

Provision Step → SailPoint ne Active Directory mein account bana diya.

action="postProvisioning" → (Jo aapke code ke bilkul end mein hai) → ServiceNow ticket ko bol diya "Closed / Completed".

