Is Pure Custom Workflow Mein Kya Badla? (Key Differences)
Koi  Nahi Hai: Aapne dhyan diya hoga, isme kahin bhi dusre workflows (Identity Request Provision ya Manage Ticket) ko call nahi kiya gaya. Saara kaam isi ke andar ho raha hai.

In-Built  Component: Approval lene ke liye humne SailPoint ka standard rule nahi lagaya, balki khud ek custom  design kiya jisme do hi button hain: Approve aur Reject.

Pure Java/BeanShell Code (): Manager ka naam nikalna ho, ServiceNow ko message bhejna ho, ya target application mein account provision karna ho—developer ne khud direct SailPoint ki internal APIs (context.getObjectByName, new Provisioner(context)) ka use karke custom code likha hai.

Badi companies mein jahan ServiceNow integration ya approval ka tarika SailPoint ke standard feature se bilkul match nahi karta, wahan developers isi tarah ka Pure Custom Workflow likhte hain.

