User ne jo Java/BeanShell code likha hai, usme teen badi technical galtiyan hain jiski wajah se SailPoint ka UI engine crash ho raha hai bina logs mein error diye:

forms.add(fv); ko do baar likh diya (Duplicate Hierarchy):
Code mein pehle field ko section mein dala gaya (sects.add(fv);), phir section ka form mein dala gaya (forms.add(sects);). Lekin uske turant baad user ne forms.add(fv); direct form par call kar diya! SailPoint mein ek Field object ek hi waqt par Section aur Form dono ka direct child nahi ho sakta. Yeh XML structure ko corrupt kar deta hai.

