Yeh workflow "On-the-Fly Dynamic Questionnaire" (mouke par sawal-jawab ka page banana) ka kaam karta hai.

QuickLink Trigger: Jab koi user ya manager SailPoint ke dashboard par kisi custom button (QuickLink) par click karega, toh yeh workflow parde ke peeche jaag uthega.

Situation Assessment (Dynamic Loop): Jaise hi yeh Generate and Display Form Step par aayega, iske andar likhi BeanShell script run hogi. Yeh script check karegi ki user ke liye is samay kitne fields zaroori hain (jaise agar user India se hai toh 3 fields dikhao, agar US se hai toh 5 fields dikhao).

Screen Generation: Yeh loop chala kar realtime mein utne text boxes (Field) taiyar karega aur bina page crash kiye user ki screen par ek sundar sa form khol dega.

Data Submission: User jab un saare fields ko bhar kar "Submit Request" button dabayega, toh data workflow ke variables mein save ho jayega aur workflow aage badhkar safely Stop ho jayega.

