Object 3: Workflow XML (Main Engine)
Yeh poora combined workflow hai. Yeh quickLinkIdentityId ka use karke target employee ka naam nikalega, use form mein lock (ReadOnly) karega aur baki 'n' number of dynamic fields generate karke screen par dikhayega.

XML
<?xml version='1.0' encoding='UTF-8'?>
