Galat Tarika: Agar aapne bade dabbe ke upar hi likh diya "Expiry Date: Kal" (Plan-Level), toh delivery boy samjhega andar ka sab kuch kal hi fenkna hai. Shampoo bhi kharab maan liya jayega.

Sahi Tarika: Aap bade dabbe par kuch mat likho. Aap andar jaakar Doodh ke packet par alag se slip chipkao (sysSunset) ki "Yeh kal khatam hoga" aur Shampoo ko waise hi rehne do (AttributeRequest Level).

Isiliye, jab bhi temporary access ka kaam ho, dates ko hamesha AttributeRequest level par set kiya jata hai taaki workflow merging ke dauran aapka temporary data safely bacha rahe.

