Aaiye aapke dono sawalon ke seedhe aur aaf jawab samajhte hain:

1. Yeh "Identity Request Provision" sach mein karta kya hai?
Definition: Yeh SailPoint ka ek standard, pehle se bana-banaya child workflow (Subprocess) hai, jiska akele kaam hai faisle ko haqeeqat mein badalna (Actual Access Deploy Karna).

Iska kaam kya hai, point-by-point dekhiye:

Approval Decisions Check Karna: Yeh sabse pehle approvalSet ko khol kar dekhta hai ki manager ne kis item ko Approve kiya hai aur kisko Reject. Jo reject ho chuki hain, unhe yahin chhod deta hai.

Connectors ko Call Karna (Automated Provisioning): Jin items ko approval mila hai (jaise Active Directory mein Administrator group dena), yeh SailPoint ke automatic connectors ko instruction bhejta hai. Connector turant AD ke server se baat karta hai aur user ka account update kar deta hai.

Manual Tickets Banana (Manual Provisioning): Agar koi aisi application hai jiska direct connector nahi hai, toh yeh un ke liye Manual Work Items taiyar karta hai aur IT Helpdesk ko email bhejta hai (manualActionsEmailTemplate="Pending Manual Changes" use karke) ki "Bhai, tum haath se access do."

2. Sabka value "Identity Request Provision" ko pass kyun ho raha hai?
Isko saare variables isliye bheje ja rahe hain kyunki access dene ke liye is child workflow ko poori kahani pata honi zaroori hai. Agar aap ise adhoora data bhejenge, toh yeh target system mein galat access daal dega ya crash ho jayega.

Aaiye dekhein ki isko har ek variable ki zaroorat kyun hai:

project aur approvalSet kyun chahiye? Iske bina isko pata hi nahi chalega ki kis chiz ka access dena hai, aur manager ne sach mein haan bola hai ya nahi. Yeh iske liye Order Sheet ki tarah hain.

identityName aur identityDisplayName kyun chahiye? Taaki isko pata rahe ki kis employee ke account mein jaakar badlav karne hain. (e.g., John ke account mein badlav karna hai, Smith ke nahi).

foregroundProvisioning aur optimisticProvisioning kyun chahiye? Taaki isko pata rahe ki access turant screen par live dikhana hai, ya background thread mein aaram se chalana hai (Speed Settings).

formTemplate aur manualActionsEmailTemplate kyun chahiye? Agar bich mein koi provisioning form dikhana pad jaye, toh uska design kya hoga, aur agar helpdesk ko mail bhejna hai toh uska format kya hoga.

launcher aur identityRequestId kyun chahiye? Auditing aur security ke liye, taaki target system ke logs mein record rahe ki yeh access kis ticket ID ke tehat aur kis ke kehne par diya gaya.

