Hierarchy Crash Fixed: User ke code mein jo forms.add(fv) do baar chalne se corrupt ho raha tha, use humne fix kiya. Ab script seedhe baseSection.add() ka use karke hierarchy ko bilkul neat aur clean rakhti hai.

Correct Sequencing: Pichle code mein XML tags ki sequence aage-piche thi (Stop step pehle aa raha tha aur Sample Form Step baad mein). Humne use sahi kiya: Start → Sample Form Step → Stop.

Smooth Integration: Ab jaise hi QuickLink trigger hoga, SailPoint Sample Workflow Form ka sancha uthayega, usme launcher ka naam bharega, 4 (ya jitni aap set karein) dynamic fields jodega aur user ki screen par bina kisi lag ke ekdam chakachak load kar dega!

