AttributeRequest attrReq Isolation: Purane code mein variables sidhe acctReq.add() ke andar fire ho rahe the jisse alag se property set nahi ho pa rahi thi. Ab har ek role/entitlement ka apna personal variable attrReq banta hai jisme sunrise aur sunset ki alag identity hoti hai.

Loop Structure Cleaning: Pehle har ek itteration par naya ProvisioningPlan banti thi, jisse pichli saari mehnat aur pichli unique dates delete ho jati thin aur sirf aakhiri entitlement hi jeeti thi. Ab new ProvisioningPlan() loop ke upar safe baitha hai aur loop ke andar sirf line-items add ho rahi hain.

