Asli Galti (Why Variables are Blank?)
User ke loop ke andar variables isliye khali aa rahe hain kyunki unhone do jagah JSON Path ki badi galatiyan ki hain:

Galat Variable Reference (Loop Block Ke Andar):
"variableA.":".loop.loopInput.name" galat hai. Loop ke andar jab hum kisi current item ko check karte hain, toh sahi syntax $.loop.context. ya direct $.loop.item ke zariye chalta hai (loopInput poori list ka context hota hai, current item ka nahi).

Email Context and Body Disconnect:
Email ke "context" block mein unhone variables toh define kiye (displayName aur employeeId), lekin unhe fetch karne ke liye trigger ka galat rasta use kiya. Agar trigger Identity Attribute Changed hai, toh sahi rasta $.trigger.identity.name ya $.identity.attributes... hoga, na ki $.getIdentity. Sath hi, Email body mein unhe double curly braces bina variable path ke fetch nahi kiya ja sakta.

