Manager ka Action: Manager ke paas request gayi, unhone dekha aur "Approve" par click kar diya.

postApproval Phase: Jaise hi manager ne sign kiya, system us purane Ticket #101 par gaya aur uska status badal kar kar diya: "Approved by Manager John on 22-May-2026. Comments: Budget approved." (Yeh postApproval hai—manager ke decision ka thappa lagana).

